In road bicycle racing, world number one Joaquim Rodríguez's Team Katusha is facing 2013 without guaranteed entries for the biggest races on the calendar after the UCI surprisingly relegated them from the 2013 UCI World Tour. (Cycling News) (Reuters via SBS)Former Danish road bicycle racer Rolf Sørensen admits in a press release that he utilised EPO and cortisone during his professional career. (Cycling News)